    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "hire_steps",
      "x": 55,
      "y": 167,
      "width": 450,
      "height": 180,
      "text": "1. Fill Identity: Hire Date, Company, Event Reason, Name, DOB, Employee ID (auto)\n2. Fill Personal Info: Name (TH/EN), Address (Province→District→Sub-District cascade), Dependents\n3. Fill Job Info: Select Position → auto-populates Org, Dept, Cost Center, Work Location\n4. Fill Compensation: Pay Component, Amount, Currency, Frequency, Pay Group\n5. Submit or Save Draft",
      "originalText": "1. Fill Identity: Hire Date, Company, Event Reason, Name, DOB, Employee ID (auto)\n2. Fill Personal Info: Name (TH/EN), Address (Province→District→Sub-District cascade), Dependents\n3. Fill Job Info: Select Position → auto-populates Org, Dept, Cost Center, Work Location\n4. Fill Compensation: Pay Component, Amount, Currency, Frequency, Pay Group\n5. Submit or Save Draft",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#475569",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
