      "id": "probation_rules",
      "x": 520,
      "y": 430,
      "width": 480,
      "height": 190,
      "text": "3 paths:\n  Pass → Set Pass Probation Date / Confirm Date in Employment Details\n  Extend → MUST update Probationary Period End Date (system warns if unchanged)\n  Unsuccessful → Triggers Termination process (CG-03-05)",
