    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "master_steps",
      "x": 55,
      "y": 767,
      "width": 450,
      "height": 180,
      "text": "Direct Edit path (no history):\n  Click pencil → Edit field → Save (Personal Info, Address, Phone, Profile data)\n\nTake Action path (with history):\n  Actions → Change Job and Comp → Select checkboxes (Job/Comp) → Set effective date\n  → Select Event + Event Reason → Update fields → Save",
      "originalText": "Direct Edit path (no history):\n  Click pencil → Edit field → Save (Personal Info, Address, Phone, Profile data)\n\nTake Action path (with history):\n  Actions → Change Job and Comp → Select checkboxes (Job/Comp) → Set effective date\n  → Select Event + Event Reason → Update fields → Save",
