    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "master_rules",
      "x": 520,
      "y": 730,
      "width": 480,
      "height": 190,
      "text": "Direct Edit = current data only, no version history, no approval (HR Admin)\nTake Action = effective-dated, creates history record, Event + Reason required\nEmployee/Manager initiated changes → require HR Admin approval\nPay Rate: Use Change Calculator (Amount or Percent), Mass upload via CSV supported\nPay Rate Events: Merit Increase, Adjust Position, Salary Cuts, Salary Adjust, Promotion",
      "originalText": "Direct Edit = current data only, no version history, no approval (HR Admin)\nTake Action = effective-dated, creates history record, Event + Reason required\nEmployee/Manager initiated changes → require HR Admin approval\nPay Rate: Use Change Calculator (Amount or Percent), Mass upload via CSV supported\nPay Rate Events: Merit Increase, Adjust Position, Salary Cuts, Salary Adjust, Promotion",
