    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "movement_steps",
      "x": 55,
      "y": 1067,
      "width": 450,
      "height": 180,
      "text": "1. Set effective date, select Event (Transfer/Promotion) and Event Reason\n2. Select target Position → org data auto-syncs\n3. Verify Organization Info, Job Info, Time Information\n4. If SSO location changes: update Compensation Info separately\n5. Click Save",
      "originalText": "1. Set effective date, select Event (Transfer/Promotion) and Event Reason\n2. Select target Position → org data auto-syncs\n3. Verify Organization Info, Job Info, Time Information\n4. If SSO location changes: update Compensation Info separately\n5. Click Save",
