      "x": 55,
      "y": 1367,
      "width": 450,
      "height": 180,
      "text": "1. Input Resigned Date, Last Date Worked\n2. Select Termination Reason (Resignation/Retirement/Dismissal/No Show/Transfer Out)\n3. Select Voluntary / Involuntary\n4. Set OK to Rehire (Yes/No)\n5. Transfer subordinates to new manager\n6. Click Save",
      "originalText": "1. Input Resigned Date, Last Date Worked\n2. Select Termination Reason (Resignation/Retirement/Dismissal/No Show/Transfer Out)\n3. Select Voluntary / Involuntary\n4. Set OK to Rehire (Yes/No)\n5. Transfer subordinates to new manager\n6. Click Save",
