    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "terminate_rules",
      "x": 520,
      "y": 1330,
      "width": 480,
      "height": 190,
      "text": "Resign = no approval workflow, HR Admin executes directly\nRetire = no workflow, system pre-populates retirement date (age 60)\nDismiss = 3-step approval workflow:\n  Initiator (LM or HRBP) → Step 1 → Step 2 → Step 3 (cross-approve LM/HRBP)\nNo Show = purges employee record from system\nTransfer Out = moves record to company outside SuccessFactors",
      "originalText": "Resign = no approval workflow, HR Admin executes directly\nRetire = no workflow, system pre-populates retirement date (age 60)\nDismiss = 3-step approval workflow:\n  Initiator (LM or HRBP) → Step 1 → Step 2 → Step 3 (cross-approve LM/HRBP)\nNo Show = purges employee record from system\nTransfer Out = moves record to company outside SuccessFactors",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#475569",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
